vote.title: An ordinance abandoning a portion of a water easement to Dallas Public Facility Corporation, the abutting owner, containing approximately 7,491 square feet of land, located near the intersection of Technology Boulevard and Connector Drive - Revenue: General Fund $11,150.00, plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee
